b>Changes<\/b>\":","DataExportTag":"Q16","QuestionID":"QID1212517622"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9RXvoU2Xl9xbrf0","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID1212517623","SecondaryAttribute":"Important: unlike a frame from the game (that depicts the complete picture) , there can be many d...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<strong>Important<\/strong>: unlike a frame from the game (that depicts the complete picture) , there can be many different frames that fit a single drop-down description.<br \/>\nFor example, in both game frames below, the agent is in lane 4, meaning that choosing the<strong>&nbsp;Lane 4<\/strong>&nbsp;drop-down option&nbsp;can have multiple occurrences.<br \/>\n<br \/>\n<b id=\"docs-internal-guid-1d1a281f-7fff-4847-4a91-3a225591b3ec\"><img height=\"148\" src=\"https:\/\/lh6.googleusercontent.com\/PnxJw7klgbc9eubEtzSmlKLiZJWt4Oi9IHLg6hlWMv1rUhEtd6tNvBaUdxGOEHJ9XYLE22eHu7d3UMXvSBxen0BrwVbjtN-R31rH1sYXoccpwC3srMyQ44UwUtjRiQoiLy7jtVNI=s0\" width=\"624\" \/><\/b><br \/>\n<br \/>\n<b id=\"docs-internal-guid-8c2bd67d-7fff-9383-11b8-becd50afd49a\"><img height=\"143\" src=\"https:\/\/lh5.googleusercontent.com\/merNsSvZYfApxQXaQ5J8luBn7RFKX55BSLhzMqFYSejSl6qBv3mxbenCUGIfB2EecEjWv3RKhCHe1F0mSVzmw1PSqqG3KE7FpnRAdA-54m9iEsAOV5I1JEcIX9bvJRHTBlLk_QNx=s0\" width=\"624\" \/><\/b>","QuestionType":"MC","Selector":"SAVR","SubSelector":"TX","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Important: unlike a frame from the game (that depicts the complete picture) , there can be many d...","Choices":[],"ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"OFF","Type":"None"}},"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"<strong>Important<\/strong>: unlike a frame from the game (that depicts the complete picture) , there can be many different frames that fit a single drop-down description.<br \/>\nFor example, in both game frames below, the agent is in lane 4, meaning that choosing the<strong>&nbsp;Lane 4<\/strong>&nbsp;drop-down option&nbsp;can have multiple occurrences.<br \/>\n<br \/>\n<b id=\"docs-internal-guid-1d1a281f-7fff-4847-4a91-3a225591b3ec\"><img height=\"148\" src=\"https:\/\/lh6.googleusercontent.com\/PnxJw7klgbc9eubEtzSmlKLiZJWt4Oi9IHLg6hlWMv1rUhEtd6tNvBaUdxGOEHJ9XYLE22eHu7d3UMXvSBxen0BrwVbjtN-R31rH1sYXoccpwC3srMyQ44UwUtjRiQoiLy7jtVNI=s0\" width=\"624\" \/><\/b><br \/>\n<br \/>\n<b id=\"docs-internal-guid-8c2bd67d-7fff-9383-11b8-becd50afd49a\"><img height=\"143\" src=\"https:\/\/lh5.googleusercontent.com\/merNsSvZYfApxQXaQ5J8luBn7RFKX55BSLhzMqFYSejSl6qBv3mxbenCUGIfB2EecEjWv3RKhCHe1F0mSVzmw1PSqqG3KE7FpnRAdA-54m9iEsAOV5I1JEcIX9bvJRHTBlLk_QNx=s0\" width=\"624\" \/><\/b>","DataExportTag":"Q17","QuestionID":"QID1212517623"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9RXvoU2Xl9xbrf0","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID1212517624","SecondaryAttribute":"Task In the next section you will be asked questions about how the system works to test your unde...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<b>Task<\/b><br>\nIn the next section you will be asked questions about how the system works to test your understanding.<br>\n<strong>These questions will grant a bonus if answered correctly.<\/strong><br>\n&nbsp;\n<div>Before continuing, you will first need to experiment with the system to understand its capabilities.<br>\nTry to understand which questions you can ask, and to understand the system's logic: how does it respond to your example specification?<br>\nThis will be helpful for the next part of the experiment.<br>\n<br>\n<b>Remember:<br>\n1)&nbsp;<\/b>Not specifying a \"Lane\" or \"Position\" means that any of them is possible.<br>\n<strong>2) <\/strong>Training isn't perfect and the videos are based on previous interactions of the agent.<br>\nThis means that some specifications might be valid, but will not find relevant video.&nbsp;<br>\n<br>\nTo check out the system, follow this link: <a href=\"https:\/\/interviewai.iem.technion.ac.il\/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">interviewai.iem.technion.ac.il<\/a>.\n<div>\n<div>Your user ID is&nbsp;<b>${e:\/\/Field\/Random_ID}<\/b><\/div>\n\n<div>Make sure to use it when specifying the frames and constraints.<\/div>\n<br>\nWhen finished, navigate to the \"<b>Done<\/b>\" page in the top bar of the system.<br>\n&nbsp;\n<div><br>\n<br>\n&nbsp;\n<div>&nbsp;<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>","QuestionType":"MC","Selector":"SAVR","SubSelector":"TX","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Task In the next section you will be asked questions about how the system works to test your unde...","Choices":[],"ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"OFF","Type":"None"}},"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"QuestionText_Unsafe":"<b>Task<\/b><br>\nIn the next section you will be asked questions about how the system works to test your understanding.<br>\n<strong>These questions will grant a bonus if answered correctly.<\/strong><br>\n&nbsp;\n<div>Before continuing, you will first need to experiment with the system to understand its capabilities.<br>\nTry to understand which questions you can ask, and to understand the system's logic: how does it respond to your example specification?<br>\nThis will be helpful for the next part of the experiment.<br>\n<br>\n<b>Remember:<br>\n1)&nbsp;<\/b>Not specifying a \"Lane\" or \"Position\" means that any of them is possible.<br>\n<strong>2) <\/strong>Training isn't perfect and the videos are based on previous interactions of the agent.<br>\nThis means that some specifications might be valid, but will not find relevant video.&nbsp;<br>\n<br>\nTo check out the system, follow this link: <a href=\"https:\/\/interviewai.iem.technion.ac.il\/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">interviewai.iem.technion.ac.il<\/a>.\n<div>\n<div>Your user ID is&nbsp;<b>${e:\/\/Field\/Random_ID}<\/b><\/div>\n\n<div>Make sure to use it when specifying the frames and constraints.<\/div>\n<br>\nWhen finished, navigate to the \"<b>Done<\/b>\" page in the top bar of the system.<br>\n&nbsp;\n<div><br>\n<br>\n&nbsp;\n<div>&nbsp;<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>","DataExportTag":"Q18","QuestionID":"QID1212517624"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9RXvoU2Xl9xbrf0","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID1212517625","SecondaryAttribute":"To progress please provide the code you received from the system that indicates you have experime...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"To progress please provide the code you received from the system that indicates you have experimented a sufficient amount:","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"TE","Selector":"SL","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"To progress please provide the code you received from the system that indicates you have experime...","Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"CustomValidation","MinChars":"1","ValidDateType":"DateWithFormat","ValidPhoneType":"ValidUSPhone","ValidZipType":"ValidUSZip","ValidNumber":{"Min":"","Max":"","NumDecimals":""},"CustomValidation":{"Logic":{"0":{"0":{"ChoiceLocator":"q:\/\/QID1212517625\/ChoiceTextEntryValue","Description":"<span class=\"ConjDesc\">If<\/span> <span class=\"QuestionDesc\">To progress please provide the unique code that indicates you have experimented a sufficient amount of times with the system:<\/span> <span class=\"LeftOpDesc\">Text Response<\/span> <span class=\"OpDesc\">Is Equal to<\/span> <span class=\"RightOpDesc\"> 895122530 <\/span>","LeftOperand":"q:\/\/QID1212517625\/ChoiceTextEntryValue","LogicType":"Question","Operator":"EqualTo","QuestionID":"QID1212517625","QuestionIDFromLocator":"QID1212517625","QuestionIsInLoop":"no","RightOperand":"895122530","Type":"Expression"},"Type":"If"},"Type":"BooleanExpression"},"Message":{"description":"Wrong answer","libraryID":"UR_81haFOwirdOynSR","messageID":"MS_6nXUHGVMFeT5Fat","subMessageID":"VE_CUSTOM_VALIDA