econdaryAttribute":"Timing","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Timing","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"t2_sum_timer","QuestionID":"QID283","QuestionType":"Timing","Selector":"PageTimer","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","MinSeconds":"0","MaxSeconds":"0"},"QuestionDescription":"Timing","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"First Click"},"2":{"Display":"Last Click"},"3":{"Display":"Page Submit"},"4":{"Display":"Click Count"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":56,"NextAnswerId":1}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9RXvoU2Xl9xbrf0","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID284","SecondaryAttribute":"Timing","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Timing","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"t2_sum_timer","QuestionID":"QID284","QuestionType":"Timing","Selector":"PageTimer","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","MinSeconds":"0","MaxSeconds":"0"},"QuestionDescription":"Timing","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"First Click"},"2":{"Display":"Last Click"},"3":{"Display":"Page Submit"},"4":{"Display":"Click Count"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":32,"NextAnswerId":1}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9RXvoU2Xl9xbrf0","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID285","SecondaryAttribute":"This is a textual summary of the agent. It describes patterns in the agent's decision-making base...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"This is a textual summary of the agent. It describes patterns in the agent's decision-making based on analysis of many agent's episodes. While reading the text, pay close attention to the following aspects: The agent\u2019s behavior and decision-making process. \nPlease read the summary fully and carefully.<br>\n<br>\n<img height=\"1000\" src=\"https:\/\/technioniit.eu.qualtrics.com\/CP\/Graphic.php?IM=IM_bchuVjilojAhvQ6\" style=\"width: 1000px; height: 1000px;\" width=\"1000\"><br>\n<br>\n<strong>Notice:<\/strong>&nbsp;After you continue to the next page you won't be able to read the textual summary again.<br><br>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"CB4_t1.2_nl","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"This is a textual summary of the agent. It describes patterns in the agent's decision-making base...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID285"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9RXvoU2Xl9xbrf0","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID286","SecondaryAttribute":"Timing","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Timing","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"t2_sum_timer","QuestionID":"QID286","QuestionType":"Timing","Selector":"PageTimer","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","MinSeconds":"0","MaxSeconds":"0"},"QuestionDescription":"Timing","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"First Click"},"2":{"Display":"Last Click"},"3":{"Display":"Page Submit"},"4":{"Display":"Click Count"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":32,"NextAnswerId":1}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9RXvoU2Xl9xbrf0","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID287","SecondaryAttribute":"This is a natural language summary of the agent, read it carefully: The RL agent's policy across...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"This is a natural language summary of the agent, read it carefully:<br \/>\n<br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size:13px;\">The RL agent&#39;s policy across 50 episodes demonstrates a consistent pattern of navigation and interaction with objects in a grid environment aimed at opening doors using keys. The agent&#39;s behavior is characterized by systematic exploration, key acquisition, and door interaction, with a focus on minimizing steps and efficiently solving the task. **Key Strategies and Objectives:<br \/>\n** 1. **Navigation:** The agent consistently moves forward, turns, and adjusts its path based on wall locations, demonstrating an understanding of the environment&#39;s structure.<br \/>\n2. **Key Interaction:** Upon identifying a key, the agent maneuvers to pick it up, showing goal-directed behavior towards objects necessary for task completion.<br \/>\n3. **Door Interaction:** After acquiring the key, the agent navigates towards the door, using the key to unlock it, which is the primary objective.<br \/>\n<br \/>\n**Patterns and Decision-Making:** - The agent follows a pattern of exploring its immediate surroundings, adjusting its path upon encountering walls, and aiming directly for keys and doors when in sight. - Decision-making is predominantly influenced by the presence of walls and doors, guiding the agent through the grid to achieve its goal.<br \/>\n&nbsp;**Efficiency Metrics:** - The episodes vary in length, with successful episodes generally characterized by direct paths to keys and doors, indicating efficient problem-solving when the environment layout is favorable. - Cumulative rewards across episodes suggest variability in performance, likely influenced by the initial placement of keys relative to the agent and the door.<br \/>\n&nbsp;**Obstacle Handling:** - The agent effectively navigates around walls, which are the primary obstacles, showing adaptability in its pathfinding algorithm.<br \/>\n&nbsp;**Comparison Across Episodes:** - Episodes where the agent quickly locates and retrieves the key, followed by successful door unlocking, achieve higher rewards and efficiency. - Longer episodes typically involve more exploration and backtracking, indicating challenges in direct pathfinding in certain grid configurations.<br \/>\n<br \/>\nIn summary, the RL agent is proficient in navigating grid environments to complete set objectives of retrieving keys and unlocking doors. Its ability to adapt its path based on environmental cues like walls and doors is evident, although its efficiency varies with the complexity of the environment layout. The agent demonstrates fundamental decision-making skills necessary for basic navigation and interaction tasks within the grid world.<\/span><br \/>\n&nbsp;<br \/>\nBased on this summary, which of the following videos best represents the agent&rsquo;s behavior?","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Q286","QuestionType":"MC","Selector":"SAVR","SubSelector":"TX","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"This is a natural language summary of the agent, read it carefully: The RL agent's policy across...","Choices":{"4":{"Display":"<video class=\"qmedia\" controls=\"true\" height=\"320\" preload=\"auto\" width=\"608\"><source src=\"https:\/\/technioniit.eu.qualtrics.com\/CP\/File.php?F=F_chlcbGe0gK2YlfL\" type=\"video\/mp4\" \/><embed align=\"middle\" autoplay=\"false\" bgcolor=\"white\" class=\"qmedia\" controller=\"true\" height=\"320\" pluginspage=\"http:\/\/www.apple.com\/quicktime\/download\/\" src=\"https:\/\/technioniit.eu.qualtrics.com\/CP\/File.php?F=F_chlcbGe0gK2YlfL\" type=\"video\/quicktime\" width=\"608\" \/><\/video>"},"5":{"Display":"<video class=\"qmedia\" controls=\"true\" height=\"320\" preload=\"auto\" width=\"608\"><source src=\"https:\/\/technioniit.eu.qualtrics.com\/CP\/File.php?F=F_7Q8OpcKBMJutrV8\" type=\"video\/mp4\" \/><embed align=\"middle\" autoplay=\"false\" bgcolor=\"white\" class=\"qmedia\" controller=\"true\" height=\"320\" pluginspage=\"http:\/\/www.apple.com\/quicktime\/download\/\" src=\"https:\/\/technioniit.eu.qualtrics.com\/CP\/File.php?F=F_7Q8OpcKBMJutrV8\" type=\"video\/quicktime\" width=\"608\" \/><\/video>\n"},"6":{"Display":"<video class=\"qmedia\" controls=\"true\" height=\"320\" preload=\"auto\" width=\"608\"><source src=\"https:\/\/technioniit.eu.qualtrics.com\/CP\/File.php?F=F_oGUNo87JpJiErd8\" type=\"video\/mp4\" \/><embed align=\"middle\" autopl