 to the key and door, despite variations in environment layouts. This suggests an underlying policy that generalizes well to different settings.<br>\n6. **Performance Metrics**: The agent's success is quantified by its ability to unlock the door within the steps provided. Episodes where the agent fails to unlock the door within the maximum allowed steps are considered unsuccessful, impacting the cumulative reward metric.<br>\n7. **Adaptation**: The agent shows an ability to adapt its strategy based on the environment's configuration. This is evident in episodes with different wall arrangements and key-door placements, where the agent adjusts its pathfinding strategy accordingly. Overall, the RL agent demonstrates effective learning and adaptation within the constraints of the given tasks, showing proficiency in navigation, object interaction, and goal achievement within a variety of simulated environments.<br>\n&nbsp;<\/span><br>\nWhich of the following agents is the one represented in the summary?","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Q321","QuestionType":"MC","Selector":"SAVR","SubSelector":"TX","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"This is a textual summary of the agent, read it carefully: The RL agent's policy across 50 episod...","Choices":{"4":{"Display":"<video class=\"qmedia\" controls=\"true\" height=\"320\" preload=\"auto\" width=\"608\"><source src=\"https:\/\/technioniit.eu.qualtrics.com\/CP\/File.php?F=F_chlcbGe0gK2YlfL\" type=\"video\/mp4\" \/><embed align=\"middle\" autoplay=\"false\" bgcolor=\"white\" class=\"qmedia\" controller=\"true\" height=\"320\" pluginspage=\"http:\/\/www.apple.com\/quicktime\/download\/\" src=\"https:\/\/technioniit.eu.qualtrics.com\/CP\/File.php?F=F_chlcbGe0gK2YlfL\" type=\"video\/quicktime\" width=\"608\" \/><\/video>"},"5":{"Display":"<video class=\"qmedia\" controls=\"true\" height=\"320\" preload=\"auto\" width=\"608\"><source s