 ability to adapt its strategy based on the environment's configuration. This is evident in episodes with different wall arrangements and key-door placements, where the agent adjusts its pathfinding strategy accordingly. Overall, the RL agent demonstrates effective learning and adaptation within the constraints of the given tasks, showing proficiency in navigation, object interaction, and goal achievement within a variety of simulated environments.<br>\n&nbsp;<\/span><br>\nWhich of the following agents is the one represented in the summary?","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"MC","Selector":"SAVR","SubSelector":"TX","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"This is a textual summary of the agent, read it carefully: The RL agent's policy across 50 episod...","Choices":{"4":{"Display":"<video class=\"qmedia\" controls=\"true\" height=\"320\" preload=\"auto\" width=\"608\"><source src=\"https:\/\/technioniit.eu.qualtrics.com\/CP\/File.php?F=F_chlcbGe0gK2YlfL\" type=\"video\/mp4\" \/><embed align=\"middle\" autoplay=\"false\" bgcolor=\"white\" class=\"qmedia\" controller=\"true\" height=\"320\" pluginspage=\"http:\/\/www.apple.com\/quicktime\/download\/\" src=\"https:\/\/technioniit.eu.qualtrics.com\/CP\/File.php?F=F_chlcbGe0gK2YlfL\" type=\"video\/quicktime\" width=\"608\" \/><\/video>"},"5":{"Display":"<video class=\"qmedia\" controls=\"true\" height=\"320\" preload=\"auto\" width=\"608\"><source src=\"https:\/\/technioniit.eu.qualtrics.com\/CP\/File.php?F=F_7Q8OpcKBMJutrV8\" type=\"video\/mp4\" \/><embed align=\"middle\" autoplay=\"false\" bgcolor=\"white\" class=\"qmedia\" controller=\"true\" height=\"320\" pluginspage=\"http:\/\/www.apple.com\/quicktime\/download\/\" src=\"https:\/\/technioniit.eu.qualtrics.com\/CP\/File.php?F=F_7Q8OpcKBMJutrV8\" type=\"video\/quicktime\" width=\"608\" \/><\/video>\n"},"6":{"Display":"<video class=\"qmedia\" controls=\"true\" height=\"320\" preload=\"auto\" width=\"608\"><source src=\"https:\/\/technioniit.eu.qualtrics.com\/CP\/File.php?F=F_oGUNo87JpJiErd8\" type=\"video\/mp4\" \/><embed align=\"middle\" autoplay=\"false\" bgcolor=\"white\" class=\"qmedia\" controller=\"true\" height=\"320\" pluginspage=\"http:\/\/www.apple.com\/quicktime\/download\/\" src=\"https:\/\/technioniit.eu.qualtrics.com\/CP\/File.php?F=F_oGUNo87JpJiErd8\" type=\"video\/quicktime\" width=\"608\" \/><\/video>"}},"ChoiceOrder":["4","5","6"],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"OFF","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":8,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"This is a textual summary of the agent, read it carefully:<br>\n<br>\n<span style=\"font-size:13px;\">The RL agent's policy across 50 episodes reveals a pattern of navigating through environments with obstacles (grey walls) and interacting with objects (keys and doors) to achieve the goal of opening a door. The agent's behavior includes:<br>\n1. **Navigation and Obstacle Avoidance**: The agent effectively navigates around grey walls, which act as obstacles. It adjusts its path dynamically based on the layout of each episode's environment.<br>\n2. **Object Interaction**: The agent identifies and moves towards keys necessary to unlock doors. Once a key is obtained, it proceeds to find and unlock the corresponding door. This demonstrates the agent's ability to link the acquisition of an item (key) with a subsequent action (unlocking).<br>\n3. **Efficient Path Selection**: The agent often takes direct paths to objectives when unobstructed, indicating a straightforward approach to goal achievement. However, it also shows adaptability by altering its path in response to walls and other barriers.<br>\n4. **Goal-Oriented Actions**: Each episode's actions are directed towards the goal of door unlocking, with movements predominantly focused on reaching keys and doors. The agent's actions are consistent with the objectives set in each environment scenario.<br>\n5. **Consistency and Learning**: Across different episodes, the agent consistently demonstrates learning by successfully navigating to the key and door, despite variations in environment layouts. This suggests an underlying policy that generalizes well to different settings.<br>\n6. **Performance Metrics**: The agent's success is quantified by its ability to unlock the door within the steps provided. Episodes where the agent fails to unlock the door within the maximum allowed steps are considered unsuccessful, impacting the cumulative reward metric.<br>\n7. **Adaptation**: The agent shows an ability to adapt its strategy based on the environment's configuration. This is evident in episodes with different wall arrangements and key-door placements, where the agent adjusts its pathfinding strategy accordingly. Overall, the RL agent demonstrates effective learning and adaptation within the constraints of the given tasks, showing proficiency in navigation, object interaction, and goal achievement within a variety of simulated environments.<br>\n&nbsp;<\/span><br>\nWhich of the following agents is the one represented in the summary?","DataExportTag":"Q329","QuestionID":"QID329"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9RXvoU2Xl9xbrf0","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID33","SecondaryAttribute":"Which of the following 3 drivers is the same driver from the previous summary?. Select you answer...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Which of the following 3 drivers is the same driver from the previous summary?. Select you answer below.<br>\n<br>\n1:<br>\n<video class=\"qmedia\" controls=\"true\" height=\"150\" preload=\"auto\" width=\"600\"><source src=\"https:\/\/technioniit.eu.qualtrics.com\/CP\/File.php?F=F_AQHsg8nhFROnvgK\" type=\"video\/mp4\"><embed align=\"middle\" autoplay=\"false\" bgcolor=\"white\" class=\"qmedia\" controller=\"true\" height=\"150\" pluginspage=\"http:\/\/www.apple.com\/quicktime\/download\/\" src=\"https:\/\/technioniit.eu.qualtrics.com\/CP\/Fil