ws an ability to adapt its strategy based on the environment's configuration. This is evident in episodes with different wall arrangements and key-door placements, where the agent adjusts its pathfinding strategy accordingly. Overall, the RL agent demonstrates effective learning and adaptation within the constraints of the given tasks, showing proficiency in navigation, object interaction, and goal achievement within a variety of simulated environments.<br>\n&nbsp;<\/span><br>\nWhich of the following agents is the one represented in the summary?","DataExportTag":"Q331","QuestionID":"QID331"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9RXvoU2Xl9xbrf0","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID332","SecondaryAttribute":"Please briefly explain your choice","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Please briefly explain your choice","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"TE","Selector":"ML","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","InputWidth":581,"InputHeight":76},"QuestionDescription":"Please briefly explain your choice","Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"RequestResponse","ForceResponseType":"RequestResponse","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"SearchSource":{"AllowFreeResponse":"false"},"QuestionText_Unsafe":"Please briefly explain your choice","DataExportTag":"t2_q3_nl_user","QuestionID":"QID332"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9RXvoU2Xl9xbrf0","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID333","SecondaryAttribute":"Please briefly explain your choice","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Please briefly explain your choice","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"t2_q2_nl_user","QuestionType":"TE","Selector":"ML","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","InputWidth":581,"InputHeight":76},"QuestionDescription":"Please briefly explain your choice","Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"RequestResponse","ForceRes